title: Allies Back Keir Starmer Amid Pressure to Resign Over Epstein Turmoil
summary_full: Senior U.K. ministers closed ranks after a senior Labour politician urged the prime minister to step down over a scandal involving an ambassador with close ties to Jeffrey Epstein.
